column5: Swiped from facebook:   If I have 10 pieces of bacon and you take 5. What do you have?       That's right, a black eye, a broken hand.... and no bacon.
you been eating with my mother-in-law again, eh Rob?
And probably a couple of stab marks from my fork.
Back in the day, we had Johnny Cash, Bob Hope and Steve Jobs...  ...now we have no cash, no hope and no jobs.   Please God, don't let Kevin Bacon die...
